# Visibility

Visibility of an emergency response location. If `Private` is set, then location is visible only for the restricted number of users, specified in `owners` array

**Properties**

| Name    | Type | Required | Description |
| :------ | :--- | :------- | :---------- |
| PRIVATE | str  | ✅       | "Private"   |
| PUBLIC  | str  | ✅       | "Public"    |
